{
  "name": "CustomProperties",
  "summary": "<p>使用 <strong>Worksheet</strong> 对象的 <strong>CustomProperties</strong> 属性返回 <strong>CustomProperties</strong> 集合。</p>\n<p>返回 <strong>CustomProperties</strong> 集合后，可根据选择向工作表和智能标记中添加元数据。</p>\n<p>若要向工作表添加元数据，请在 <strong>Add</strong> 方法中使用 <strong>CustomProperties</strong> 属性。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*在此示例中，ET 向活动工作表添加标识符信息，并向用户返回名称和值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Add metadata to worksheet.</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomProperties</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Market&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Nasdaq&quot;</span>)\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Display metadata.</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> customProperty = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomProperties</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(customProperty.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span> + <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;\\t&quot;</span> + customProperty.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例设置第一张工作表第一个标识符的值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomProperties</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;World&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>由代表附加信息的 <strong>CustomProperty</strong> 对象组成的集合，这些信息可用作 XML 的元数据。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 **<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Application/Application .htm#Application.Application\">Application</a>**对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个表示指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该���象的应用程序）创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>){\n\t<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n\t<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>) {\n\t\t<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n\t}\n\t<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n\t\t<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n\t}\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Count",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Long</strong> 值，它代表集合中对象的数量。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示活动工作表标识符数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomProperties</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Add",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>添加自定义属性信息，返回一个代表自定义属性信息的 **<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/CustomProperty/CustomProperty .htm#CustomProperty.CustomProperty\">CustomProperty</a>**对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例向活动工作表添加标识符信息，并将其名称和值返回给用户*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Add metadata to worksheet.</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomProperties</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Market&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Nasdaq&quot;</span>)\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Display metadata.</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> customProperty = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomProperties</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(customProperty.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span> + <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;\\t&quot;</span> + customProperty.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例向第一张工作表添加标识符信息。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomProperties</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Test2&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;hello&quot;</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Name",
          "type": "string",
          "description": "<p>自定义属性的名称。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        },
        {
          "name": "Value",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>自定义属性的值。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        }
      ],
      "returns": "<p>一个 CustomProperty 对象，表示自定义属性信息。</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "name": "Item",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>从集合中返回一个对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*在此示例中，ET 向活动工作表添加标识符信息，并向用户返回名称和值*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Add metadata to worksheet.</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomProperties</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Market&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Nasdaq&quot;</span>)\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Display metadata.</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> customProperty = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomProperties</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(customProperty.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span> + <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;\\t&quot;</span> + customProperty.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例设置第一张工作表第一个标识符的名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomProperties</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Test1&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Index",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>对象的名称或索引号。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        }
      ],
      "returns": "CustomProperty"
    }
  ]
}